properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 9 at 11:41AM CST until February 10 at 6:00PM CST by NWS New Orleans LA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Frequent gusts 30 to 34 knots this afternoon, then seas
building to 5 to 7 ft tonight into Monday.

* WHERE...Portions of Gulf of Mexico.

* WHEN...Until 6 PM CST Monday.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 PM CST MONDAY
